title: 820-4924 = doesn't start, no post, no chime, 105mA
message:
Board is clean and no previous work has been done. DCPS pulls 105mA.

These are missing rails:
PP1V2_S3_CPUDDR
PP1V2_S3
PP0V6_S0_DDRVTT
PPVTTDDR_S3

On U7400, EN pins are present as well as V5IN.

title: 820-4924 = doesn't start, no post, no chime, 105mA
message:
Check diode mode to ground at L7430.
Do you get 1V8_S3?

title: 820-4924 = doesn't start, no post, no chime, 105mA
820-4924 = doesn't start, no post, no chime, 105mA
message:
Inspect traces, solders and resistors around U7400.
Be sure R/C7425 are good.
If all OK, change U7400; maybe need to change Q7430 too.

title: 820-4924 = doesn't start, no post, no chime, 105mA
message:
All around U7400 was good. Checked traces and solder. Ended up changing U7400 and it works!
Milion thanks 2informaticos!
